```

- %OPTION% `line 5, because lion cannot be reassigned a value`
- %OPTION% `line 6, because the += operator cannot be used with the undefined variable bear`
- %OPTION% `line 5, because the prefix (++) operator does not exist in JavaScript`
- %OPTION% `line 3, because the variable bear is left undefined`

